## .gitignore for BlindMatchPAS

# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# User-specific files
*.userprefs

# NuGet
*.nupkg
**/packages/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

# ASP.NET Core
**/wwwroot/lib/

# SQLite
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# Environment / Secrets
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/*.pfx
**/*.env

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.sln.docstates

# Rider
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log
